01:03.188 --> 01:05.106
grain of sand

01:05.148 --> 01:09.778
around which has formed

01:05.148 --> 01:09.778
the pearl of my renaissance.

01:09.820 --> 01:12.113
I like me again.

01:12.155 --> 01:13.949
Cadet!

01:16.451 --> 01:20.873
