04:34.733 --> 04:37.527
so you'll be seeking it from me.

04:37.569 --> 04:39.654
Look elsewhere, son.

04:41.073 --> 04:43.283
Who's the anal-retentive

04:41.073 --> 04:43.283
outsider?

04:44.451 --> 04:48.329
With repressed matricidal

04:44.451 --> 04:48.329
tendencies?

04:48.371 --> 04:51.083
It was from me, sir!

04:48.371 --> 04:51.083
Please, stop.

04:52.375 --> 04:54.128
As you may or may not know,

04:54.169 --> 04:56.337
I was once one of you...

04:54.169 --> 04:56.337
a Krelboyne,

04:56.379 --> 04:58.173
and I'm sure I would have made

04:56.379 --> 04:58.173
the same

04:58.215 --> 05:00.217
lame attempt

04:58.215 --> 05:00.217
to ingratiate myself

05:00.259 --> 05:03.262
to the new, soft-headed thickwit

05:00.259 --> 05:03.262
teaching my class.

