05:09.977 --> 05:11.061
"you set your mind to.

05:11.103 --> 05:14.022
It must be so easy being you."

05:14.064 --> 05:14.982
Well, bull ...!

05:15.023 --> 05:16.775
(all gasp)

05:16.817 --> 05:20.612
All that gets you is an ex-wife

05:16.817 --> 05:20.612
and $14 million in debt.

05:20.654 --> 05:22.739
Now I refuse to let you fall

05:20.654 --> 05:22.739
into the trap

05:22.781 --> 05:23.949
society has set for you.

05:23.991 --> 05:25.826
Playtime is over children.

05:25.867 --> 05:28.078
You've had a free ride so far.

05:28.120 --> 05:30.831
It's about time somebody

05:28.120 --> 05:30.831
motivated you, challenged you,

05:30.872 --> 05:32.958
tested your mental limits.

05:33.000 --> 05:34.042
Granted, I don't have

05:34.084 --> 05:35.376
a teaching certificate

05:35.418 --> 05:36.670
from a two-year

05:35.418 --> 05:36.670
community college

05:36.711 --> 05:39.089
like most of the people

05:36.711 --> 05:39.089
I was forced to say hello to

05:39.131 --> 05:40.841
this morning

05:39.131 --> 05:40.841
in the teachers lounge,

05:40.882 --> 05:43.468
but, you know, I'm just going

05:40.882 --> 05:43.468
to try to muddle through

05:43.510 --> 05:46.054
with my double doctorate

05:43.510 --> 05:46.054
from Harvard.

05:46.096 --> 05:48.223
This is a test.

05:48.265 --> 05:49.390
Correct. You have 20 minutes.

05:49.432 --> 05:51.392
There are six

05:49.432 --> 05:51.392
essay questions.

05:51.434 --> 05:54.395
I'm sorry. I thought this was

05:51.434 --> 05:54.395
the gifted class.

05:54.437 --> 05:55.897
Begin!

06:09.161 --> 06:10.704
Thanks for the ride.

06:10.745 --> 06:12.831
Are you sure

06:10.745 --> 06:12.831
