06:22.841 --> 06:25.426
I don't have to justify

06:22.841 --> 06:25.426
myself to you.

06:25.468 --> 06:27.804
I don't have to justify

06:25.468 --> 06:27.804
myself to anyone.

06:27.846 --> 06:29.514
That's why

06:27.846 --> 06:29.514
I got emancipated, okay?

06:29.556 --> 06:31.141
Okay.

06:31.183 --> 06:33.352
Good luck with your parents.

06:33.392 --> 06:35.103
Yeah, well, they had

06:33.392 --> 06:35.103
