06:35.145 --> 06:36.355
We'll see how they take it.

06:37.647 --> 06:39.900
(growling)

06:41.318 --> 06:42.610
(shrieks)

06:42.652 --> 06:44.445
You...!

06:44.487 --> 06:48.449
(screaming)

06:44.487 --> 06:48.449
(growling)

06:48.491 --> 06:50.369
You ungrateful

06:48.491 --> 06:50.369
son of a...!

06:54.164 --> 06:55.916
This wasn't meant

06:54.164 --> 06:55.916
to hurt you!

06:55.957 --> 06:58.377
After all we've done!

07:05.424 --> 07:07.094
(screams)

07:13.892 --> 07:16.353
All I'm saying

07:13.892 --> 07:16.353
is that you can get

07:13.892 --> 07:16.353
your diploma first

07:16.395 --> 07:17.771
and then do

07:16.395 --> 07:17.771
what you want.

07:17.812 --> 07:20.481
It's all about maximizing

07:17.812 --> 07:20.481
your options,

07:20.523 --> 07:22.734
taking the long view.

07:22.776 --> 07:25.070
Sorry about using

07:22.776 --> 07:25.070
"The Closer."

07:25.112 --> 07:26.113
Nonsense.

07:26.154 --> 07:27.488
I wouldn't have

07:26.154 --> 07:27.488
taught it to you

07:27.530 --> 07:28.865
if I didn't want

07:27.530 --> 07:28.865
you to use it.

07:28.907 --> 07:30.200
Listen, what do

07:28.907 --> 07:30.200
I always say?

07:30.242 --> 07:31.201
"The nards

07:30.242 --> 07:31.201
are fair game."

