Look, sometimes

07:34.454 --> 07:35.914
you're presented

07:35.956 --> 07:37.582
with an opportunity

07:35.956 --> 07:37.582
that you just can't pass up.

07:37.624 --> 07:39.500
I hope you understand.

07:39.542 --> 07:40.710
I'm not the one you

07:39.542 --> 07:40.710
have to worry about.

07:40.752 --> 07:42.087
I know. And I want

07:42.129 --> 07:43.380
to get this straight

07:42.129 --> 07:43.380
with Mom.

07:43.422 --> 07:45.173
That's why I came here.

07:45.215 --> 07:46.507
Okay then.

07:46.549 --> 07:47.467
Honey?

07:49.386 --> 07:52.347
Um, your son has something

07:49.386 --> 07:52.347
