But, since this is

08:14.577 --> 08:16.997
the  gifted  class,

08:17.038 --> 08:20.125
I also factored in

08:17.038 --> 08:20.125
cogency of argument,

08:20.167 --> 08:21.542
economy of language

08:21.584 --> 08:25.422
