08:34.681 --> 08:36.557
But we all still have As?

08:36.599 --> 08:38.559
Of course.

08:38.601 --> 08:40.187
So, what does

08:38.601 --> 08:40.187
being number one get you?

08:40.228 --> 08:41.729
Nothing.

08:41.771 --> 08:44.024
Just the knowledge that you...

08:44.065 --> 08:45.566
are number one.

08:45.608 --> 08:47.486
Or that you are not...

08:47.527 --> 08:48.778
number one.

08:50.613 --> 08:51.823
