If I ever start

09:04.294 --> 09:06.171
acting like that,

09:06.213 --> 09:08.006
you have to promise

09:06.213 --> 09:08.006
to kill me.

09:08.048 --> 09:10.175
No, no more death pacts.

09:10.217 --> 09:11.592
Don't worry about it.

09:11.634 --> 09:13.011
The only way

09:11.634 --> 09:13.011
that stupid board

09:13.053 --> 09:15.055
can have an effect

09:13.053 --> 09:15.055
