09:15.096 --> 09:16.515
Those numbers mean nothing.

09:18.641 --> 09:19.809
What are...

09:19.851 --> 09:21.019
you doing?

09:21.061 --> 09:22.603
Nothing.

09:22.645 --> 09:24.314
You were studying?

09:24.356 --> 09:25.482
No, I wasn't.

09:25.524 --> 09:28.151
My book just fell open

09:25.524 --> 09:28.151
