09:47.379 --> 09:49.506
It's really inspiring.

09:49.548 --> 09:51.508
What are you looking at?

09:51.550 --> 09:52.633
Francis.

09:52.675 --> 09:54.886
He's still out there?

09:54.928 --> 09:56.637
Yeah, he's eating

09:54.928 --> 09:56.637
