10:47.814 --> 10:48.940
I really missed you.

10:48.982 --> 10:50.066
(grunts)

10:50.108 --> 10:51.943
What was that for?

10:51.985 --> 10:53.153
Emancipation?

10:53.194 --> 10:55.196
