11:02.787 --> 11:04.581
but we would never abandon her.

11:04.623 --> 11:05.957
I'm not abandoning her.

11:05.999 --> 11:07.708
I'm just going to Alaska.

11:07.750 --> 11:09.544
That's 5,000 miles away.

11:09.586 --> 11:10.711
It is not...

11:10.753 --> 11:12.130
5,000 miles,

11:10.753 --> 11:12.130
are you serious?

11:12.172 --> 11:13.714
Oh, my God, it's going

11:13.756 --> 11:15.592
to take me forever

11:13.756 --> 11:15.592
to get up there.

11:15.634 --> 11:16.717
Then don't go.

11:16.759 --> 11:18.136
Guys, you have to understand.

11:18.178 --> 11:19.929
I'm not doing this

11:18.178 --> 11:19.929
to hurt anybody.

11:19.971 --> 11:21.640
I just... I really think

11:21.680 --> 11:24.184
this is my best chance

11:21.680 --> 11:24.184
to make something of myself.

