Tell it to Mom.

11:25.435 --> 11:27.228
I can't, she

11:25.435 --> 11:27.228
won't talk to me.

11:27.270 --> 11:28.813
She is being

11:27.270 --> 11:28.813
so immature.

11:28.855 --> 11:32.400
In the meantime, I'm stuck

11:28.855 --> 11:32.400
outside in the freezing cold.

11:33.776 --> 11:35.820
Would it be all right

11:33.776 --> 11:35.820
if I slept in here tonight?

11:40.699 --> 11:41.784
Certainly, the whale

11:41.826 --> 11:44.162
represents

11:41.826 --> 11:44.162
the search for God...

11:44.204 --> 11:45.830
but that could be limiting.

11:45.872 --> 11:47.332
We could say it was

11:47.374 --> 11:49.000
the search

11:47.374 --> 11:49.000
for the self.

11:49.042 --> 11:49.959
Melville could be

11:50.001 --> 11:51.961
considered a pre-existentialist.

11:54.797 --> 11:56.007
But you can't deny

11:56.049 --> 11:58.259
that the whale could also

11:56.049 --> 11:58.259
be the search for truth

11:58.301 --> 11:59.760
which has been

11:58.301 --> 11:59.760
a theme throughout

11:59.802 --> 12:00.845
his whole oeuvre.

12:05.642 --> 12:09.770
But we can't overlook the fact

12:05.642 --> 12:09.770
that it is an actual whale,

12:09.812 --> 12:12.440
which was the

12:09.812 --> 12:12.440
biggest industry

12:09.812 --> 12:12.440
in the 19th century.

12:12.482 --> 12:13.774
The oil was

12:12.482 --> 12:13.774
used in lamps,

12:13.816 --> 12:15.734
soaps and even cosmetics.

12:18.863 --> 12:22.783
Today, whaling is outlawed,

12:18.863 --> 12:22.783
but many Aleutian islanders

12:22.825 --> 12:26.787
are legally allowed

12:22.825 --> 12:26.787
to harvest whales

12:26.829 --> 12:29.290
for ritual purposes.

12:29.999 --> 12:32.460
But I digress!

12:32.502 --> 12:34.421
(whimpering)

12:34.462 --> 12:37.798
Wow, nine places.

12:37.840 --> 12:39.634
That's got to be a record.

12:41.094 --> 12:43.096
Okay, on to new business.

12:43.137 --> 12:45.473
This Friday,

12:43.137 --> 12:45.473
Principal Littledove

12:45.515 --> 12:47.975
will be dropping by

12:45.515 --> 12:47.975
for a little evaluation.

12:48.017 --> 12:50.395
I think he'll be very impressed

12:48.017 --> 12:50.395
with what he sees.

12:50.437 --> 12:52.980
I don't think

12:50.437 --> 12:52.980
he'll understand it,

12:53.022 --> 12:54.815
but I think his tiny brain

12:54.857 --> 12:57.860
will have the dim perception

12:54.857 --> 12:57.860
of the progress you can make

12:57.902 --> 13:01.864
when students

12:57.902 --> 13:01.864
are properly motivated.

13:01.906 --> 13:03.824
Now, who would like

13:01.906 --> 13:03.824
to sink their teeth

13:03.866 --> 13:05.285
into some

13:03.866 --> 13:05.285
Bernoulli equations?

13:10.039 --> 13:11.291
Come on, guys.

13:11.332 --> 13:12.459
Look at yourselves.

13:12.500 --> 13:13.710
If we don't let those

13:13.752 --> 13:15.712
stupid rankings get to us,

13:13.752 --> 13:15.712
they mean nothing.

13:15.754 --> 13:18.214
Easy for you

13:15.754 --> 13:18.214
to say, Number One.

13:18.256 --> 13:19.507
I have a name.

13:19.549 --> 13:21.134
We all have names!

13:21.175 --> 13:24.011
Oh, my God,

13:21.175 --> 13:24.011
I can't remember mine!

13:24.053 --> 13:25.555
MALCOLM:

13:24.053 --> 13:25.555
This is ridiculous!

13:25.597 --> 13:28.433
School used to be the one place

13:25.597 --> 13:28.433
where you were truly happy,

13:28.475 --> 13:30.393
and Herkabe has taken that

13:28.475 --> 13:30.393
away from you.

13:31.102 --> 13:32.228
That stupid board

13:32.270 --> 13:33.229
is ruining our lives.

13:33.271 --> 13:34.439
We can't let him do that.

13:34.481 --> 13:37.358
What choice... do we have?

13:37.400 --> 13:39.944
We have the choice that

13:37.400 --> 13:39.944
people have had for centuries.

13:39.986 --> 13:42.238
We can choose to fail.

13:42.280 --> 13:43.906
Like the French?

13:43.948 --> 13:47.952
You mean... we tank...

13:43.948 --> 13:47.952
today's test?

13:47.994 --> 13:50.079
No, we don't tank it.

13:50.121 --> 13:51.790
We nuke it.

13:52.707 --> 13:54.292
Every answer wrong.

13:54.334 --> 13:55.876
No complete sentences.

13:55.918 --> 13:57.878
No punctuation.

13:57.920 --> 14:00.881
And we use number three pencils.

14:00.923 --> 14:01.716
(gasping)

14:01.758 --> 14:03.050
You can't rank zeros!

14:03.092 --> 14:04.177
That's brilliant!

14:04.218 --> 14:05.261
He'll have no choice

14:05.303 --> 14:07.138
but to throw out

14:05.303 --> 14:07.138
his stupid system!

14:07.180 --> 14:08.889
We'll be free!

14:08.931 --> 14:11.434
(cheering)

14:15.730 --> 14:17.898
I'm very disappointed in you.

14:17.940 --> 14:20.777
Everyone else, nice job.

14:35.875 --> 14:36.917
(softly):

14:35.875 --> 14:36.917
I'm sorry.

14:36.959 --> 14:38.919
(softly):

14:36.959 --> 14:38.919
I'm sorry.

14:38.961 --> 14:40.338
I tried.

14:40.380 --> 14:42.382
My hand wouldn't let me.

14:42.423 --> 14:45.552
I regret...

14:45.593 --> 14:46.927
nothing.

14:46.969 --> 14:48.929
Interesting gambit, but I guess

14:48.971 --> 14:51.932
the Lemmings didn't follow you

14:48.971 --> 14:51.932
off the cliff.

14:51.974 --> 14:54.185
When you've spent some time

14:51.974 --> 14:54.185
in the real world,

14:54.227 --> 14:58.022
you'll realize you can't fight

14:54.227 --> 14:58.022
the system, and now...

14:58.064 --> 14:59.691
I'm  the system.

15:12.078 --> 15:13.204
(exasperated sigh)

15:15.874 --> 15:17.792
Don't worry,

15:15.874 --> 15:17.792
I just let the air out.

15:17.834 --> 15:19.960
We can talk

15:17.834 --> 15:19.960
while I put on your spare.

15:20.002 --> 15:22.046
Look, I'm sorry I had

15:20.002 --> 15:22.046
to resort to this,

15:22.088 --> 15:25.383
but you have to give me

15:22.088 --> 15:25.383
five minutes so we can talk.

15:25.425 --> 15:26.384
(engine starts)

15:26.426 --> 15:27.343
(music blaring)

15:27.385 --> 15:29.596
(yelling):

15:27.385 --> 15:29.596
I can talk over the music!

15:31.013 --> 15:32.807
You can't drive on a flat!

15:34.016 --> 15:36.310
You're going to ruin your rims!

15:39.021 --> 15:40.440
(tires squealing)

15:40.481 --> 15:42.650
That was a red light!

15:43.943 --> 15:45.653
You might want to notice

15:45.695 --> 15:48.989
my entire opening paragraph

15:45.695 --> 15:48.989
is a palindrome.

15:49.031 --> 15:50.991
You might want to notice...

15:51.033 --> 15:52.952
my formatting.

15:57.749 --> 15:58.999
What's this?

15:59.041 --> 16:01.669
A study of irrigation techniques

15:59.041 --> 16:01.669
of pre-Roman society and how

16:01.711 --> 16:04.004
they led to the advancement

16:01.711 --> 16:04.004
of Western civilization.

16:04.046 --> 16:07.007
I thought we were just studying

16:04.046 --> 16:07.007
Mesopotamian farming techniques.

16:07.049 --> 16:08.008
We were.

16:08.050 --> 16:10.052
I just used that as

16:08.050 --> 16:10.052
a jumping-off point.

16:10.094 --> 16:12.722
I saw how their influences

16:10.094 --> 16:12.722
spread through the Egyptians,

16:12.764 --> 16:15.934
the Carthaginians, basically

16:12.764 --> 16:15.934
through the whole ancient world.

16:15.975 --> 16:18.018
I think you'll be very happy

16:15.975 --> 16:18.018
with this paper.

16:18.060 --> 16:20.605
Very nice, Number Twelve.

16:20.647 --> 16:24.233
It's nice to see

16:20.647 --> 16:24.233
a little effort put forth

16:24.275 --> 16:28.988
while some are content

16:24.275 --> 16:28.988
to do the absolute minimum.

16:30.740 --> 16:35.035
So... he wants... to play.

16:35.077 --> 16:37.622
Oh, we'll play all right.

16:37.664 --> 16:40.082
What is it we're playing?

16:40.124 --> 16:44.044
♪ ♪

17:11.113 --> 17:14.408
♪ ♪

17:43.062 --> 17:44.397
Okay, I think

17:43.062 --> 17:44.397
we're ready

17:44.438 --> 17:46.190
to show Principal

17:44.438 --> 17:46.190
Littledove

17:46.232 --> 17:49.402
what the right kind

17:46.232 --> 17:49.402
of motivation

17:46.232 --> 17:49.402
can accomplish.

17:49.443 --> 17:51.779
Well done, class.

17:56.242 --> 18:00.038
You know, maybe we should

17:56.242 --> 18:00.038
just put our heads down

18:00.079 --> 18:03.082
and take a rest

18:00.079 --> 18:03.082
for a moment, shall we?

18:07.211 --> 18:09.005
Yes, One-to-the-Eleventh?

18:09.047 --> 18:11.424
Did you know I can count

18:09.047 --> 18:11.424
to a million by prime numbers?

18:11.465 --> 18:12.926
I can, too!

18:12.967 --> 18:15.135
So can I! It's easy.

18:15.177 --> 18:16.429
That's not necessary.

18:16.470 --> 18:19.807
2, 3, 5, 7, 11...

18:19.849 --> 18:21.726
13, 17, 19...

18:21.768 --> 18:23.937
(frantically):

18:21.768 --> 18:23.937
23, 29, 31.

18:23.978 --> 18:25.730
Now by hundreds!

18:25.772 --> 18:31.235
101, 211, 307, 401, 503, 601...

18:31.277 --> 18:32.236
DABNEY:

18:31.277 --> 18:32.236
7!

18:32.278 --> 18:35.155
7! No!

18:35.197 --> 18:37.157
Okay, that is enough,

18:35.197 --> 18:37.157
One-to-the-Eleventh.

18:37.199 --> 18:39.159
By thousands! 1,009...

18:39.201 --> 18:40.160
2,003...

18:40.202 --> 18:41.161
Now back by hundreds!

18:41.203 --> 18:43.163
2,111, 2,203...

18:43.205 --> 18:44.248
2... 11...

18:44.290 --> 18:46.166
No!

18:46.208 --> 18:47.668
Where are you going,

18:46.208 --> 18:47.668
Number Three?

18:47.710 --> 18:48.878
It's hot.

18:48.920 --> 18:51.839
It's hot and I'm stupid!

18:51.881 --> 18:54.174
I'm stupid, too!

18:54.216 --> 18:55.175
(screaming)

18:55.217 --> 18:57.136
Everybody, please remain seated!

18:58.096 --> 18:59.680
I'm Zero!

19:00.848 --> 19:03.392
Zero-to-the-Zeroth!

19:03.434 --> 19:05.144
(screaming)

19:06.270 --> 19:08.940
(screaming)

19:15.237 --> 19:17.406
I'm nothing!

19:17.448 --> 19:20.367
I'm invisible!

19:20.409 --> 19:21.619
(whistles)

19:21.661 --> 19:24.288
Boy, that's quite a show

19:21.661 --> 19:24.288
for your first week here.

19:24.330 --> 19:27.667
You were right,

19:24.330 --> 19:27.667
you can't beat the system,

19:27.708 --> 19:29.961
but you sure can break it.

19:33.965 --> 19:35.591
I love you guys.

19:35.633 --> 19:38.218
I'll write you

19:35.633 --> 19:38.218
when I get there, okay?

19:38.260 --> 19:40.054
Someday, when

19:38.260 --> 19:40.054
you come back

19:40.096 --> 19:44.224
and you're unemployed

19:40.096 --> 19:44.224
and have no place to live,

19:44.266 --> 19:47.186
you can come stay at my castle.

19:48.980 --> 19:50.982
Thanks, bud.

19:51.983 --> 19:53.317
He's leaving.

19:53.359 --> 19:55.319
He just wants to talk to you.

19:55.361 --> 19:57.237
Just hear him out.

19:57.279 --> 20:00.282
Lois, this... this

19:57.279 --> 20:00.282
has got to stop.

20:00.324 --> 20:02.035
He's going very far away

20:02.076 --> 20:05.245
and you're not

20:02.076 --> 20:05.245
going to see him

20:02.076 --> 20:05.245
for a very long time.

20:06.789 --> 20:09.291
Honey, there are

20:06.789 --> 20:09.291
moments in life

20:09.333 --> 20:13.129
that you just

20:09.333 --> 20:13.129
don't get back,

20:09.333 --> 20:13.129
and I know you.

20:13.171 --> 20:15.255
If you do not deal

20:13.171 --> 20:15.255
with this now,

20:15.297 --> 20:17.800
it will haunt

20:15.297 --> 20:17.800
you  forever.

20:21.303 --> 20:22.346
Fine.

20:22.388 --> 20:27.226
I've lost a son

20:22.388 --> 20:27.226
but gained a baby.

20:30.021 --> 20:32.065
I tried.

20:32.106 --> 20:34.358
I know.

20:40.322 --> 20:42.533
Are you sure

20:40.322 --> 20:42.533
this is what you want?

20:42.575 --> 20:45.745
Well, it'd better be.

20:47.413 --> 20:49.040
LOIS:

20:47.413 --> 20:49.040
Francis.

20:59.967 --> 21:01.719
I'm listening.

21:04.222 --> 21:05.305
This is what you get!

21:05.347 --> 21:07.975
This is what you get for

21:05.347 --> 21:07.975
the way you treated me!

21:08.017 --> 21:11.353
I'm going to Alaska

21:08.017 --> 21:11.353
and you're going to

21:08.017 --> 21:11.353
be left without a son!

21:11.395 --> 21:13.313
And the horrible

21:11.395 --> 21:13.313
way you treated me

21:13.355 --> 21:14.815
is now a matter

21:13.355 --> 21:14.815
of public record!

21:14.857 --> 21:16.776
LOIS:

21:14.857 --> 21:16.776
I treated  you?!

21:16.817 --> 21:18.945
We've made sacrifice

21:16.817 --> 21:18.945
after sacrifice for you

21:18.986 --> 21:20.613
and you've caused us

21:18.986 --> 21:20.613
nothing but pain!

21:20.654 --> 21:22.322
You want pain?! I've

21:20.654 --> 21:22.322
got your scars, baby!

21:22.364 --> 21:24.200
3h years in that

21:22.364 --> 21:24.200
horrible school...

21:24.242 --> 21:26.035
We went without

21:24.242 --> 21:26.035
for that school!

21:26.077 --> 21:26.994
Oh!

21:27.036 --> 21:28.746
Oh! Maybe I should

21:27.036 --> 21:28.746
thank you!

21:28.788 --> 21:31.958
Thank you, Mother,

21:28.788 --> 21:31.958
for making my life

21:28.788 --> 21:31.958
a living hell!

21:31.999 --> 21:33.251
Living hell?!

21:31.999 --> 21:33.251
You've been nothing

21:33.292 --> 21:35.169
but a problem since

21:33.292 --> 21:35.169
the day you were born.

21:35.211 --> 21:37.213
Your problems are over, lady,

21:35.211 --> 21:37.213
'cause I'm out of here!
